<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-10">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">How We Bill</h1>

  <p class="mb-6">
    <span class="font-medium">replicate.info</span> is priced annually. One flat invoice based on your team size. No metering. No surprise mid-cycle upgrades. Just clear pricing for engineering leaders who want their team to level up, fast.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-6">
    Invoices are sent by email via Stripe with full remittance details. Pay by card, ACH, or wire - <span class="font-semibold">Net 30</span>.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-10">
    Pre-pay future years for <span class="font-semibold">20%</span> off today's prices. Email <a href="mailto:procurement@replicate.info" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-semibold">procurement@replicate.info</a> for an invoice.
  </p>

  <div class="grid gap-2 mb-12 border border-gray-200 rounded-md overflow-hidden text-sm shadow">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 border-b border-gray-200">
      <div class="px-4 py-2 font-semibold">Team Size</div>
      <div class="px-4 py-2"><span class="font-semibold">Annual Price</span> (USD)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 border-b border-gray-100"><div class="px-4 py-2">Up to 5 engineers</div><div class="px-4 py-2">$3,000</div></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 border-b border-gray-100"><div class="px-4 py-2">Up to 10 engineers</div><div class="px-4 py-2">$5,000</div></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 border-b border-gray-100"><div class="px-4 py-2">Up to 25 engineers</div><div class="px-4 py-2">$10,000</div></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 border-b border-gray-100"><div class="px-4 py-2">Up to 75 engineers</div><div class="px-4 py-2">$20,000</div></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 border-b border-gray-100"><div class="px-4 py-2">Up to 150 engineers</div><div class="px-4 py-2">$40,000</div></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 border-b border-gray-100"><div class="px-4 py-2">Up to 300 engineers</div><div class="px-4 py-2">$80,000</div></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 border-b border-gray-100"><div class="px-4 py-2">Up to 1,000 engineers</div><div class="px-4 py-2">$100,000</div></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2"><div class="px-4 py-2">Unlimited Usage</div><div class="px-4 py-2">$300,000</div></div>
    <div class="px-4 py-2 text-sm border-t border-gray-200 bg-neutral-100 md:text-center rounded-bl-md rounded-br-md">
      <span class="font-medium">VAT may be added at checkout</span>, depending on your location. We do not charge US sales tax.
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mb-1 font-semibold">Your first full calendar month is free.</p>
  <p class="mb-4">No credit card required. No sales demos (unless you want one).</p>

  <p class="mb-1 font-semibold">Your price is fixed for the year.</p>
  <p class="mb-4">Just one fixed, non-refundable annual invoice (Net 30). If the team grows past your current tier, great, they can still use the product. Just renew at a higher tier next year. No mid-year surprises. We trust you.</p>

  <p class="mb-1 font-semibold">No auto-renewals.</p>
  <p class="mb-4">We'll email you 30 days before your term ends. No auto-renewal. No auto-invoicing. Renewal requires explicit confirmation from the account owner.</p>

  <p class="mb-1 font-medium">No redlines, vendor portals, or negotiations.</p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    <a href="/w9.pdf" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">W-9</a>,
    <a href="/dpa.pdf" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">DPA</a>, and
    <a href="/msa.pdf" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">MSA</a> are standardized. Email <a href="mailto:procurement@replicate.info" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">procurement@replicate.info</a> if you'd like signable versions.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-1 font-medium">Refund Policy</p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    We do not offer refunds once an invoice is paid, even if usage stops. We'll gladly help fix duplicate or erroneous payments.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-1 font-medium">Support</p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Email support (<a href="mailto:support@replicate.info" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@replicate.info</a>) is included for all tiers. Typical response time is under 24 hours.
  </p>

  <p class="text-gray-500 mt-10">
    <%= link_to 'Terms of Service', '/terms', class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline" %> &nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp;
    <%= link_to 'Privacy Policy', '/privacy', class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline" %> &nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp;
    <%= link_to 'Security', '/security', class: "text-blue-600 hover:underline" %>
  </p>
</div>